<emphasis box="[198,397,152,177]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">Female genitalia</emphasis>
: Seventh sternite with V-shaped excavation on hind margin. Second pair of valvula with smooth margined teeth, distal cutting edge occupying about 
<number box="[857,909,190,216]" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" value="0.47">0.47</number>
of valvulae.
</paragraph>
